瓜地馬拉的鐵路修建於1880年和1930年之間，總里程885千米，曾經有鐵路连接邻国[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]、[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]的[[圣安娜省|圣安娜省]]，現已荒廢。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.puertochiapas.com.mx/news/362-railway-between-guatemala-and-mexico-connectivity-across-puerto-chiapas |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-09-15 |archive-date=2020-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200622040200/https://www.puertochiapas.com.mx/news/362-railway-between-guatemala-and-mexico-connectivity-across-puerto-chiapas |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[瓜地馬拉市|瓜地馬拉市]]第一區及[[克萨尔特南戈|克萨尔特南戈]]有鐵道博物館，可以懷念過去瓜國的鐵道時光。<ref>{{Cite news | url= http://www.tramz.com/gt/q.html | title= Ferrocarril de Los Altos Quezaltenango Electric Railway GUATEMALA | publisher= tramz.com | date= 2020-08-20 | language= en | accessdate= 2020-09-15 | archive-date= 2020-02-20 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200220010040/http://www.tramz.com/gt/q.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>

另外，危地马拉政府计划在2021年開始修建日运输量250,000人次的{{Internal link helper/en|危地马拉城轻轨|Metro Riel}}線路。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.masterbuilder.co.in/guatemala-city-will-tender-700m-light-rail-scheme-2017/|title=Guatemala City will tender $700m light rail scheme by 2017|date=31 October 2016|access-date=2020-09-18|archive-date=2016-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161115032906/http://www.masterbuilder.co.in/guatemala-city-will-tender-700m-light-rail-scheme-2017/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.railjournal.com/regions/central-south-america/guatemala-city-lrt-right-of-way-agreement-signed/|title=Guatemala City LRT right-of-way agreement signed|date=31 July 2019|accessdate=31 July 2019|archive-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731230011/https://www.railjournal.com/regions/central-south-america/guatemala-city-lrt-right-of-way-agreement-signed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

